      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning purist is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mechanically flawless, having recently undergone a comprehensive valve adjustment and a preventative VANOS overhaul to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains incredibly taut, with a factory-perfect floor pan and reinforced subframe mounting points. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-Differential lock, providing unparalleled tactile feedback. The original Laguna Seca Blue finish retains deep luster, and the interior bolsters show zero compression wear. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era.",
