      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained to remain in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster, protected by a high-end ceramic coating with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections to be found. Every panel gap is laser-straight, reflecting its accident-free history and climate-controlled garage storage. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or trim rattles. All electronic components, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, revealing a service history that has been followed to the letter using only OEM parts. The car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example that requires zero investment and is ready for the most rigorous inspection.",
